  // equality (==/!=/===/!==), prefix \`!\`, parenthesised grouping, and the
  // JSON-ish literals (numbers, strings, true/false/null/undefined). No
  // arithmetic, no logical &&/||, no <,>, no calls. Parse failures and
  // missing-path lookups both return undefined so a partially-arrived
  // mid-stream expression can't crash the surrounding render — the
  // text-walker's missing-val placeholder takes over.
  //
